The '''Turkish Under 20 and Under 21 national basketball team''' (Turkish Young Women national basketball team), ('''{{lang-tr|Ãmit Milli Basketbol TakÄ±mÄ±}}''') is the representative for [[Turkey]] in international [[basketball]] competitions, and it is organized and run by the [[Turkish Basketball Federation]]. The '''Turkish Under 20 Women national basketball team''' represents Turkey at the [[FIBA Europe Under-20 Championship for Women]] and the '''Turkish Under 21 Women national basketball team''' at the [[FIBA Under-21 World Championship for Women]].
